#: src/Admin/Settings.php:41
msgid "Shortlist Settings"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:42
msgid "Shortlist"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid "Give shoppers an accessible \"save for later\" wishlist. Choose where the button appears, tune the labels, and design the list shown on the My Account tab, the [shortlist] shortcode, and the Shortlist block."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:118
msgid "General"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:120
msgid "Turn the wishlist on and decide who can use it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:127
msgid "Enable wishlist"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:128
msgid "Let visitors add products to a wishlist."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:129
msgid "Master switch. When off, no buttons, menu item, shortcode or block output is rendered anywhere on your store - nothing is deleted, so you can switch it back on at any time."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:135
msgid "Allow guests"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:136
msgid "Allow logged-out visitors to build a wishlist."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:137
msgid "Guest lists are stored in a cookie and automatically merged into the customer account on login, so nothing is lost. Turn this off to require an account first - logged-out shoppers are then sent to the login page when they click the button."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:147
msgid "Button placement"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:149
msgid "Pick where the add-to-wishlist button and the My Account tab appear."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:156
msgid "Single product page"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:157
msgid "Show the add-to-wishlist button on the product page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:158
msgid "Adds the toggle button to the product summary, just under the add-to-cart area."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:163
msgid "Shop and archive loops"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "Show the add-to-wishlist button on product cards in the shop loop."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Adds a full-width toggle to each product card on the shop, category and tag pages so shoppers can save without opening the product."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:170
msgid "My Account menu"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:171
msgid "Add a \"Wishlist\" tab to the WooCommerce My Account area."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:172
msgid "Gives logged-in customers a dedicated Wishlist tab in My Account that lists everything they have saved."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:177
msgid "Show item count"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:178
msgid "Show the number of saved items next to the My Account \"Wishlist\" menu label."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:179
msgid "Appends a live count, e.g. \"Wishlist (3)\", to the menu label so customers see at a glance how many items they have saved. Requires the My Account menu option above."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:188
msgid "Button labels"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:190
msgid "The text shown on the toggle button. It switches between the two as items are saved and removed."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:197
msgid "Add label"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:198
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:469
#: src/Service/ShortlistService.php:54
msgid "Add to wishlist"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:199
msgid "Shown when the product is not yet saved. Leave blank to use the default \"Add to wishlist\"."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:204
msgid "Remove label"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:205
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:470
#: src/Service/ShortlistService.php:55
#: templates/account-wishlist.php:30
msgid "Remove from wishlist"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:206
msgid "Shown once the product is saved, so clicking again removes it. Leave blank to use the default \"Remove from wishlist\"."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:215
msgid "Wishlist list"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:217
msgid "Design the list shown on the My Account tab and via the [shortlist] shortcode and the Shortlist block."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:224
msgid "List heading"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:225
#: templates/account-wishlist.php:20
msgid "My wishlist"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:226
msgid "The heading shown above the saved products. Only displayed when \"Show heading\" below is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:231
msgid "Intro text"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:232
msgid "e.g. Items you saved for later"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:233
msgid "Optional short paragraph shown under the heading - a good place to reassure shoppers their list is private to them. Leave blank to hide it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:238
msgid "Empty-list message"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:239
#: templates/account-wishlist.php:22
msgid "Your wishlist is empty."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:240
msgid "Friendly message shown when the shopper has not saved anything yet. A \"Browse products\" link is added automatically below it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:245
msgid "Columns"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:246
msgid "How many products sit side by side in the grid (1-6). The layout automatically drops to a comfortable number of columns on small screens."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:251
msgid "Show heading"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:252
msgid "Show the list heading above the products."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:253
msgid "Toggles the \"List heading\" above. Turn off if your page already has its own title."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:258
msgid "Show image"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:259
msgid "Show the product thumbnail."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:260
msgid "Displays each saved product's featured image. Space is reserved for it so the page never jumps as images load."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:265
msgid "Show name"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:266
msgid "Show the product name."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:267
msgid "Displays the product title as a link to the product page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:272
msgid "Show price"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:273
msgid "Show the product price."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:274
msgid "Displays the current price, including any sale price, exactly as WooCommerce formats it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:279
msgid "Show add-to-cart"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:280
msgid "Show an add-to-cart button for in-stock products."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:281
msgid "Lets shoppers move an item straight from their wishlist to the cart. The button is only shown for purchasable, in-stock products."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:286
msgid "Show remove button"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:287
msgid "Show a remove-from-wishlist button on each item."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:288
msgid "Adds a one-click remove button to each saved product so shoppers can tidy their list."
msgstr ""

